  <title>Настройка контрастности</title>

  <p>You can adjust the contrast of windows and buttons so that they're easier
  to see. This is not the same as <!--display-dimscreen is a stub. Please add
  the link back when it's unstubbed.-Aruna<link xref="display-dimscreen">-->
  changing the brightness of the whole screen; only parts of the
  <em>user interface</em> will change.</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Click your name on the top bar and select <gui>Settings</gui>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Откройте <gui>Специальные возможности</gui> и выберите вкладку <gui>Зрение</gui>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Включите переключатель <gui>Высокая контрастность</gui>.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <note style="tip">
    <p><link xref="a11y-icon">accessibility icon</link> on the top bar and
    selecting <gui>High Contrast</gui>.</p>
  </note>

